{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GudRhC3vTR4XUGxbeFkbXF","type":"tool_result","content":"commit ed31df6e62e6bbfe6273cc4e63855b1f0c39df98\nAuthor: lucas <lucas@perfectlunacy.com>\nDate:   Fri Mar 13 09:55:38 2026 -0700\n\n    Move run grouping/sorting from client-side JS to server-side Go\n    \n    The initial page load showed a flat list that jumped around when the\n    client-side JS reorganized it. Move the filtering (list-tasks exclusion),\n    sorting (running first, then by started_at desc), and task grouping\n    logic into a server-side groupAndSortRuns function used by both the HTML\n    handler and the JSON API. The client JS now just renders pre-grouped\n    entries from the server.\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n internal/adapters/web/handler.go          | 112 ++++++++++++++++++++-\n internal/adapters/web/handler_test.go     |  47 +++++----\n internal/adapters/web/templates/runs.html | 160 +++++-------------------------\n 3 files changed, 160 insertions(+), 159 deletions(-)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01W2hdAPWRtb8iwNr2VUPxQ9","session_id":"2f5b3a10-2c53-4a3a-a212-5498e6e5d993","uuid":"6f5e8a0e-4efb-4865-bb5f-9cbdf8a36438"}
